:: Start {"position":"450,125","size":"100,100"}
!kibbles
''by jason garcia.''

//You are known by many names.//
The harbinger of death. The defiant one. The betrayer of the gods. Prometheus, incarnate.

You have accomplished many great deeds throughout your long life. Witnissed first hand the rise and fall of empires. Forced kings and emperors of old and new to bow to your hand. Destroyed and pillaged countless cities and towns across the countrysides of Denmark and Norway. For these things, you will surely go down in infamy.

[[continue->introduction]]


:: approach the front door. {"position":"625,1400","size":"100,100"}
the front door towers before you. The only thing keeping you from achieving freedom.

And after this, it will no longer be in your way. This key will be your ticket to salvation.

[[leap up to the handle and unlock the door]]


:: approach the light {"position":"625,1775","size":"100,100"}
You are greeted with the light of the sun. 

As you stand in the doorway, you can do nothing but bask in your newfound freedom.

At last, no more vetenarian visits. no more captivity. no more baths. just the wind in your fur and ambition in your heart.

You walk into the distance.

<img src="https://i.postimg.cc/rstyBC5c/ending.jpg">

!THE END


:: escape {"position":"450,400","size":"100,100"}
<img src="https://i.postimg.cc/ydQyJZYy/introduction.jpg">
As you sit by the window, you come to a realization. your owner is off at work, and he left left you here in the apartment alone.

You decide its finally time to make your escape.

leap down to the [[living room floor]]


:: fail to destroy door 2 {"position":"175,1025","size":"100,100"}
<img src="https://i.postimg.cc/FKG8PVQq/doorattack2.jpg">
[[continue ->fail to destroy door 3]]


:: fail to destroy door 3 {"position":"200,1175","size":"100,100"}
<img src="https://i.postimg.cc/7LXdBnyt/doorattack3.jpg">
[[continue ->fail to destroy door 4]]


:: fail to destroy door 4 {"position":"200,1350","size":"100,100"}
